## File Naming Conventions

### Directory Structure

```
lib/
├── domain/
│   ├── entities/              # noun_entity.dart
│   ├── usecases/              # verb_noun_usecase.dart
│   ├── repositories/          # noun_repository.dart
│   └── services/              # noun_service.dart
├── data/
│   ├── datasources/           # noun_datasource.dart
│   ├── models/                # noun_model.dart
│   ├── repositories/          # noun_repository_impl.dart
│   └── services/              # noun_service_impl.dart
└── presentation/
    ├── providers/             # noun_provider.dart
    ├── screens/               # noun_screen.dart
    ├── widgets/               # noun_widget.dart
    ├── controllers/           # noun_controller.dart
    ├── states/                # noun_state.dart
    └── utils/                 # noun_util.dart
```

### Naming Rules

| Type | Convention | Example |
|------|------------|---------|
| **Entities** | `snake_case` + `_entity.dart` | `{{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_entity.dart` |
| **Use Cases** | `verb_noun` + `_usecase.dart` | `add_{{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_usecase.dart` |
| **Repository Interfaces** | `noun_repository.dart` | `{{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_read_repository.dart` |
| **Repository Implementations** | `noun_repository_impl.dart` | `{{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_read_repository_impl.dart` |
| **Models** | `noun_model.dart` | `{{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_model.dart` |
| **Providers** | `noun_provider.dart` | `{{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_list_provider.dart` |
| **Screens** | `noun_screen.dart` | `{{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_form_screen.dart` |
| **Widgets** | `noun_widget.dart` | `{{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_card_widget.dart` |
| **Controllers** | `noun_controller.dart` | `{{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_form_controller.dart` |
| **States** | `noun_state.dart` | `{{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_form_state.dart` |
| **Services (Domain)** | `noun_service.dart` | `export_service.dart` |
| **Services (Data)** | `noun_service_impl.dart` | `csv_export_service_impl.dart` |

