## Code Formatting

### Line Length

- **Maximum line length**: 80 characters (soft limit), 120 characters (hard limit)
- **Use trailing commas** for multi-line parameters and arguments

```dart
// ✅ GOOD - Trailing comma
final result = await useCase.execute(
  {{PRIMARY_ENTITY}}Entity(
    amount: state.nominal,
    type: state.type,
    dateTime: DateTime(
      state.date.year,
      state.date.month,
      state.date.day,
      state.time.hour,
      state.time.minute,
    ),
    {{SECONDARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}Id: state.{{SECONDARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}Id,
    note: state.note,
    createdAt: DateTime.now(),
  ),
);

// ❌ BAD - Too long, no trailing comma
final result = await useCase.execute({{PRIMARY_ENTITY}}Entity(amount: state.nominal, type: state.type, dateTime: DateTime(state.date.year, state.date.month, state.date.day, state.time.hour, state.time.minute), {{SECONDARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}Id: state.{{SECONDARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}Id, note: state.note, createdAt: DateTime.now()));
```

### Indentation

- **2 spaces** for indentation (no tabs)
- **Cascades** (`..`) for method chaining on same object

```dart
// ✅ GOOD - Cascades
final container = AppGlassContainer.glassCard(
  child: Column(
    children: [
      Text('Title'),
      Text('Subtitle'),
    ]
      ..addAll(
        items.map((item) => Text(item)).toList(),
      ),
    ],
  ),
);

// ❌ BAD - Repetitive container reference
final container = AppGlassContainer.glassCard(
  child: Column(
    children: [
      Text('Title'),
      Text('Subtitle'),
    ],
  ),
);
container.child = Container(/* ... */);
```

### Optional Parameters

```dart
// ✅ GOOD - Required positional parameters first, then optional
class {{PRIMARY_ENTITY}}Entity {
  const {{PRIMARY_ENTITY}}Entity({
    required this.amount,      // Required
    required this.type,        // Required
    this.id,                   // Optional
    this.note,                 // Optional
  });
}

// ❌ BAD - Optional parameters before required
class {{PRIMARY_ENTITY}}Entity {
  const {{PRIMARY_ENTITY}}Entity({
    this.id,                   // Optional first
    required this.amount,      // Required after
    required this.type,
  });
}
```

