### Test File Naming

```
test/
├── unit/                      # Unit tests (domain layer)
│   ├── domain/
│   │   ├── usecases/
│   │   │   └── add_{{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_usecase_test.dart
│   │   └── entities/
│   │       └── {{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_entity_test.dart
├── widget/                    # Widget tests (presentation layer)
│   └── presentation/
│       └── screens/
│           └── {{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_form_screen_test.dart
└── integration/               # Integration tests
    └── features/
        └── {{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_flow_test.dart
